				<td colspan="2"><span>My guild is now elemental.  It was a huge goal for us to take a small (60 members tops) guild with no Ssra basement of Vex Thal gear and make it Elemental Plane capable and we did it!  So, having reached the goal, I decided to step down as raid leader, at least for awhile.   All that is the very upbeat and satisfying setup to the story.
<br />

<br />
So last night, we have 40 people on (its summer - numbers still down a bit) and we decide it's time to start banging on the elemental named so we head into Reef of Coirnav because I really have researched that zone and know my way around to assist our puller.  We're after Hydrotha as I know we can handle him and he's a great place to start.  We're at zone in, making groups when I go linkdead -- and so has everyone else in the guild.  And other guilds.  Yes, Luclin server has crashed!  And of course, POP named, for the most part, do not spawn on a server reset.
<br />

<br />
Sony, you bastages owe me one Abalone Engraved Tribal Mask!!!</span></td>
