Catching the spawn is really not the problem.  On Luclin, we have 6 or 7 guilds who are beyond elementals and rarely kill anything but the occasional flagging whack of the gods.  Only 3 guilds are in the elementals and farming/XPing there so it isn't that hard for us to hit Hydrotha on a raid night -- two weeks worth of raids, two Hydrotha kills.  This last one, Hydrotha dropped two pairs of chain sleeves.  The good news is, it put a ranger below me on points.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
